        <comments>When a POSH case is arbitrarily moved to the Cancelled status, implement a script to:&#13;
&#13;
Create an incident in the Incident Management table with the following details:&#13;
Caller: current.u_victim&#13;
Short Description: current.u_short_notes&#13;
Description: current.u_detailed_description&#13;
Assignment Group: dc0db135c332010016194ffe5bba8f23 (Incident Management Team)&#13;
Save the incident's sys_id in the POSH record's u_incident field.&#13;
Display a confirmation message:&#13;
"This POSH request has been escalated as: [Incident Number]".&#13;
Ensure data integrity and redirect the user appropriately.</comments>
